{"tid":1998104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國大波人妻飲精液smoothie 防肺炎","createTime":"2020-05-02T07:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T01:15:56.000Z","uid":229185,"like":23,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"c942bf01ccfba011dca27be374759d892cedbf75","tid":1998104,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eVS5HRs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeVS5HRs.jpg&h=15616a45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMum drinks sperm smoothies to fight off coronavirus<br />\nA mother-of-two believes that drinking smoothies with a shot of sperm have helped to boost her immune system and is helping prevent coronavirus.<br />\n<br />\nTracy Kiss, 32, says she&rsquo;s not had a cold or flu for three years because of her concoction which is made using donations from her boyfriend and she takes three shots a week.<br />\n<br />\nTracy, a personal trainer from Aylesbury, said: &lsquo;I found a free and vegan-friendly alternative method to boost the body&rsquo;s immune system. You don&rsquo;t always know what is in pharmaceutical medicine &ndash; it is much better for the body to drink something that doesn&rsquo;t contain chemicals.<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;It isn&rsquo;t much different to a mother breastfeeding her newborn to give them the nutrients they need. It isn&rsquo;t for everyone but it is packed full of vitamins and I haven&rsquo;t had a cold or flu ever since drinking it in 2017 &ndash; I also put it on my face to clear up my skin.&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://metro.co.uk/2020/05/01/mum-drinks-sperm-smoothies-fight-off-coronavirus-12639469/\" data-sr-url=\"ht